primary_outcome.description:
1.1. In women admitted to care between years 2013-2017, the trend in the:
distribution of ages;
proportion of late presenters (CD4).
proportion that start ART during the first year after admission;
schemes of ART used for the first ART.
1.2. Proportion of women alive, retained to care, retained to ART, and with virologic suppression at one year of follow up, from admissions occurred in 2016.
